data.description: Spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home on a nice corner lot in Pecan Lakes. With some TLC in the form of new carpet or LVP in the bedrooms and a fresh coat of paint, this is a great opportunity for instant equity. Generous layout, ample living space, breakfast area and dining room, stainless appliances, step-up ceilings, master bathroom with soaking tub and separate shower, covered back porch, fenced yard, and more. Priced to accommodate cosmetic updates.
